node.text:
Drifting around on Forza Horizon 4 in a BMW 1M, with 100% exhaust sound. Hope you guys enjoy it, let me know if you want me to do more of these! I do daily Story clips w/ music, here I'll post a more unedited version!
Thanks for the support #BoostSquad ❤️

node.text:
1039 HP Sequential GTR r32 reaction 😂🔥 you know the car is on point when it makes a man scream for his life 💯
N1 RB26 Block.
-Spool 2.8L Stroker kit
-CP Pistons
-Precision 7675 Gen2 and much much more.
Can you guess how many PSI that turbo was pushing? 🤔
🔌 Follow me @boostlust for the best modified cars around the world 🔌
🚗 @builtby_blake
🛠 @deanbuczynski
